  "prompt": "A symbolic oil painting tapestry blending scenes from a man's life journey. In one corner, a philosopher's apartment in Schwabing, richly adorned, with a white-haired elder sleeping in a well-lit, book-lined living room. Adjacent to it, a young man in leather, cataloging VHS tapes in a dim bedroom studio. Below, a dusty bicycle leans against a pub with a glowing Irish sign, a man seated inside gripping a familiar leather jacket from a stranger. At center, two men share a king-size bed—one wearing a collarbone sling, the other helping gently, no shame, only care. In the lower left, a tent beneath trees, a campfire lit; a cat watches nearby. In the top right, a freighted mountain bike winds through Alpine paths into northern Italy. And in the background, subtly woven through everything, an open book glows faintly with the words 'Eloi, Eloi.' The overall mood is reflective, textured, and warm — like memory rendered in brushstroke.",
